    <string name="about_text">Alpha Sound™ was created by Adrian Majewski."\n""\n"Description:"\n"This app is a simple music player, which
        does not require Internet connection to work. It is minimalistic,
        there are no features like equalizer, etc. It simply loads any music
        file from the external storage of your phone. It has also notification player so you can
        change or pause song without unlocking your device."\n""\n"Have fun :)</string>

    <string name="instruction_text"> The application was created for Android 5.1.1 (Lollipop) or higher.
        If you try to run it on earlier version than Lollipop it will probably crush, or just won\'t work properly. But you
    can try, choice is yours."\n""\n"Instruction:"\n"Use it like any other music player, there is nothing special about this one.</string>

